<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20081120022905/http://www.cul-studies.com/english/interview/200512/3226.html">The Two Hats of Partha Chatterjee: An Interview</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.today/20030728201514/http://www.scholars.nus.edu.sg/post/poldiscourse/chatterjee/chatterjeeov.html">Partha Chatterjee: Colonialism, History and Civil Society</a></li>
<li>
<a rel="nofollow" class="external autonumber" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080303091604/http://www.asiasource.org/news/special_reports/chatterjee.cfm">[1]</a> Towards a Postcolonial Modernity - Asiasource Interview with Partha Chatterjee</li>
</ul>
